---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Shipping and Delivery Policy | Bablon">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="bg-white shadow-sm rounded-lg p-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-black mb-8 border-b pb-4">
        Shipping and Delivery Policy
      </h1>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-gray-800">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black mb-4">Introduction</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            At Bablon, we understand that timely delivery is crucial for your
            furniture shopping experience. This Shipping and Delivery Policy
            outlines our delivery procedures, timelines, and what you can expect
            when ordering from us.
          </p>
          <p>
            We partner with reliable logistics providers to ensure your
            furniture reaches you safely and on time.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black mb-4">Delivery Areas</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            We currently offer delivery to the following areas:
          </p>
          <div class="ml-4 mb-4">
            <p class="mb-2">
              <span class="font-medium">Metro Cities:</span> Mumbai, Delhi, Bangalore,
              Chennai, Kolkata, Hyderabad, Pune, Ahmedabad
            </p>
            <p class="mb-2">
              <span class="font-medium">Tier 1 Cities:</span> Jaipur, Lucknow, Chandigarh,
              Indore, Bhopal, Nagpur, Surat, Vadodara
            </p>
            <p class="mb-2">
              <span class="font-medium">Tier 2 Cities:</span> Most major cities and
              towns across India
            </p>
            <p>
              <span class="font-medium">Remote Areas:</span> Delivery available to
              most remote areas with additional charges
            </p>
          </div>
          <p>
            Please check your delivery address during checkout to confirm
            delivery availability and any additional charges.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black mb-4">
            Delivery Timelines
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4">Our standard delivery timelines are as follows:</p>
          <div class="ml-4 mb-4">
            <p class="mb-2">
              <span class="font-medium">In-Stock Items:</span> 3-7 business days
              for metro cities, 5-10 business days for other cities
            </p>
            <p class="mb-2">
              <span class="font-medium">Made-to-Order Items:</span> 15-30 business
              days depending on complexity
            </p>
            <p class="mb-2">
              <span class="font-medium">Custom Furniture:</span> 20-45 business days
              based on specifications
            </p>
            <p class="mb-2">
              <span class="font-medium">Assembly Required:</span> Additional 1-2
              business days for assembly services
            </p>
            <p>
              <span class="font-medium">Express Delivery:</span> Available for select
              items with 1-3 business day delivery
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black mb-4">
            Shipping Charges
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            Our shipping charges are calculated based on the following factors:
          </p>
          <div class="ml-4 mb-4">
            <p class="mb-2">
              <span class="font-medium">Free Shipping:</span> Orders above ₹10,000
              to metro cities
            </p>
            <p class="mb-2">
              <span class="font-medium">Standard Shipping:</span> ₹500-₹1,500 depending
              on location and item size
            </p>
            <p class="mb-2">
              <span class="font-medium">Express Shipping:</span> ₹1,000-₹2,500 for
              faster delivery
            </p>
            <p class="mb-2">
              <span class="font-medium">Remote Areas:</span> Additional charges may
              apply for delivery to remote locations
            </p>
            <p>
              <span class="font-medium">Heavy Items:</span> Additional charges for
              items requiring special handling
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black mb-4">
            Order Processing
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4">Once you place an order, here's what happens:</p>
          <div class="ml-4 mb-4">
            <p class="mb-2">
              <span class="font-medium">Order Confirmation:</span> You'll receive
              an email confirmation within 1 hour
            </p>
            <p class="mb-2">
              <span class="font-medium">Processing:</span> Orders are processed within
              1-2 business days
            </p>
            <p class="mb-2">
              <span class="font-medium">Shipping Notification:</span> You'll receive
              tracking information once shipped
            </p>
            <p class="mb-2">
              <span class="font-medium">Delivery Updates:</span> Regular updates
              on delivery status via SMS and email
            </p>
            <p>
              <span class="font-medium">Delivery Confirmation:</span> Final confirmation
              once item is delivered
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black mb-4">
            Delivery Process
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4">On the day of delivery:</p>
          <div class="ml-4 mb-4">
            <p class="mb-2">
              • Our delivery team will contact you 1-2 hours before arrival
            </p>
            <p class="mb-2">
              • Please ensure someone is available to receive the delivery
            </p>
            <p class="mb-2">
              • Have your order confirmation and ID ready for verification
            </p>
            <p class="mb-2">
              • Inspect the item thoroughly before signing the delivery receipt
            </p>
            <p>• Report any damage immediately to the delivery team</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black mb-4">
            Assembly Services
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            We offer professional assembly services for furniture that requires
            assembly:
          </p>
          <div class="ml-4 mb-4">
            <p class="mb-2">
              <span class="font-medium">Assembly Fee:</span> ₹300-₹800 depending
              on item complexity
            </p>
            <p class="mb-2">
              <span class="font-medium">Timing:</span> Assembly is typically completed
              on the same day as delivery
            </p>
            <p class="mb-2">
              <span class="font-medium">Warranty:</span> Assembly work is covered
              under our service warranty
            </p>
            <p>
              <span class="font-medium">Requirements:</span> Clear space and access
              to the room where furniture will be placed
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black mb-4">
            Delivery Exceptions
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4">Delivery may be delayed or rescheduled due to:</p>
          <div class="ml-4 mb-4">
            <p class="mb-2">• Adverse weather conditions</p>
            <p class="mb-2">• Natural disasters or emergencies</p>
            <p class="mb-2">
              • Unavailability of recipient at delivery address
            </p>
            <p class="mb-2">• Inaccessible delivery locations</p>
            <p class="mb-2">• Vehicle breakdowns or logistics issues</p>
            <p>• Public holidays or restricted movement days</p>
          </div>
          <p>
            We will notify you immediately of any delays and reschedule at your
            convenience.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black mb-4">
            Failed Deliveries
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4">If delivery fails due to recipient unavailability:</p>
          <div class="ml-4 mb-4">
            <p class="mb-2">
              • We will attempt delivery again the next business day
            </p>
            <p class="mb-2">
              • Three failed attempts will result in return to warehouse
            </p>
            <p class="mb-2">
              • A restocking fee of ₹500 may apply for returned items
            </p>
            <p>
              • You can reschedule delivery by contacting our customer service
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black mb-4">
            Delivery Tracking
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4">Track your order through multiple channels:</p>
          <div class="ml-4 mb-4">
            <p class="mb-2">• Order tracking page on our website</p>
            <p class="mb-2">• SMS updates at key delivery milestones</p>
            <p class="mb-2">• Email notifications with tracking links</p>
            <p>• Customer service support for tracking inquiries</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black mb-4">
            Contact Information
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4">For delivery-related inquiries, please contact us:</p>
          <div class="ml-4 mb-4">
            <p class="mb-2">• Email: delivery@bablon.in</p>
            <p class="mb-2">• Phone: [Your Phone Number]</p>
            <p>• WhatsApp: [Your WhatsApp Number]</p>
          </div>
          <p>
            Please have your order number ready when contacting us for faster
            assistance.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black mb-4">Policy Updates</h2>
          <p>
            We reserve the right to modify this Shipping and Delivery Policy at
            any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting on our
            website. We encourage you to review this policy periodically.
          </p>
        </section>

        <div class="border-t pt-6 mt-2.5 text-sm text-gray-600">
          <p>Last Updated: May 16, 2025</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

